                        <h2>8. Learn a Valuable Skill</h2>
                        <img class="indeximg" src="/uploads/2023/9/digital-marketing-ai-prompt-1200x.webp" alt="Digital marketing prompt">
                        <p>One of the most profitable uses of AI is to learn skills that increase your earning potential. ChatGPT can tell you the most in-demand skills and even teach you itself.</p>
                        <p>Ask ChatGPT to recommend high-value skills that are growing in popularity and pay well. It may suggest coding, digital marketing, data science, copywriting, languages and more.</p>
                        <p>Then start doing research about the skill you are interested in, once you come across certain questions that are not answered by searching on google, try asking ChatGPT!</p>
                        <p>The more valuable skills you add to your resume, the more money you can make either as an employee or running your own business.</p>
